{"id": 2002, "genre": 1004, "title": "你的“电话恐惧症”到几级了？来测！", "description": "你会对打电话这件事紧张吗？或者说，对说话这件事就很紧张。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 18422, "comment_count": 115, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171109114543ZAJj0CNgUHOSKLX2.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 6, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-25T17:00:24Z", "column": null, "normal_questions": [{"id": 3263, "content": "对于陌生来电，你的第一反应通常是：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 247846, "title": "本能地先挂断", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/201711131106434BtNfA75brmlPxzG.jpg"}, {"id": 247847, "title": "我有快递or外卖吗？", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113110736lfck1IeH8uxTmRJM.jpg"}, {"id": 247851, "title": "不情愿地接起来", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113110927jFTWesilJM2mr79K.png"}, {"id": 247852, "title": "啥都不想直接接听", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113110947ydplZCh4ke8bgTOt.png"}]}, {"id": 3264, "content": "周末约朋友吃饭，需要预定个餐厅，你的习惯更接近：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 247873, "title": "尽量挑能线上订的", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113113718fX1M70VkoCZbngWe.jpg"}, {"id": 247871, "title": "不能线上订再电话", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113113431nXkrxoqAjWfg1tGu.jpg"}, {"id": 247857, "title": "直接搜电话打过去", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113111334r1F2A0toGjsUHCDN.jpg"}, {"id": 247872, "title": "挑个不用排队的", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113113154kvUTeRr4JF3sDNaf.jpg"}]}, {"id": 3265, "content": "临时需要联系其他部门同事说个事，查到对方手机号之后，你更倾向于：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 247886, "title": "少废话，打过去", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113122220DyHPejZ6YlfcTRgk.jpg"}, {"id": 247887, "title": "组织下语言打过去", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113122213OMbVo4WS095HRIvL.jpg"}, {"id": 247889, "title": "在微信里搜搜看", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/201711131222369UKRs46bl0yQciSj.jpg"}, {"id": 247890, "title": "还是……邮件吧", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113122229FAPVbyQXSs67G1tU.jpg"}]}, {"id": 3266, "content": "接完朋友打来的寒暄聊天电话，大部分时候你的状态更接近：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 248055, "title": "聊得很开心呐", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116114923WG9ZPNC4M1siJluk.png"}, {"id": 248053, "title": "刚才漏说了一个事", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116114859ECoVUiMJ43NzPksH.png"}, {"id": 248052, "title": "终于完事儿了", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116114849RNtrKJHp102Z4Thn.png"}, {"id": 248054, "title": "我的内心毫无波澜", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116114911o9hwxiA1n4IKc5SW.png"}]}, {"id": 3267, "content": "你最近拨出去的电话多数都是：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 249299, "title": "除了快递外卖没了", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171117144007JlNgMWY6a0EpbnmS.png"}, {"id": 249301, "title": "大部分是工作同事", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171117143723sNMwU4q5jro6R9YX.jpg"}, {"id": 249303, "title": "一多半是家人对象", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/201711171435345khfVmMUEFKA1RSG.jpg"}, {"id": 249304, "title": "间或有几个朋友", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171117143419LmlaHxFIDXBkAVUG.jpg"}]}, {"id": 3268, "content": "新加微信的朋友突然开始用语音和你说话，你更可能：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 248140, "title": "坚持用文字和ta聊", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171113171113X9iAKzT5byfDW6SP.jpg"}, {"id": 249148, "title": "很勉强地转成语音", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/2017111611353741qflSNo02B3KmHD.jpg"}, {"id": 249149, "title": "自然换成语音", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116113551AOhHdxISE9J40Glj.jpg"}, {"id": 249150, "title": "我就是那个用语音的", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116113624DxJzHrAidq3n2Q5S.jpg"}]}, {"id": 3269, "content": "通常在什么情况下，你会把手机设置成“勿扰模式”？", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 249287, "title": "不设", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116175419jOptF42o1GJKUbn6.png"}, {"id": 249288, "title": "睡觉的时候", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116175427az6io9kAsVXnqGpU.png"}, {"id": 249289, "title": "任何“想静静”的时候", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/201711161754332APDsJf3rMCvqxcd.png"}, {"id": 249290, "title": "几乎一直勿扰", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116175441KTpehoBXvAn6N8Vz.png"}]}, {"id": 3270, "content": "你对飞机上不能用手机这件事怎么看：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 249273, "title": "好事儿，难得清静", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116151625XGHTs5SOLVghqI8p.jpg"}, {"id": 249274, "title": "无所谓，怎样都行", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116151650a5Q6bKlquN2Pz3xS.png"}, {"id": 249275, "title": "不开心，忍不住", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116151719CwVNf1SDUAlzBX6e.jpg"}, {"id": 249276, "title": "这个规定不合理", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116151742KUBtD61HTfFLquvY.jpg"}]}, {"id": 3271, "content": "约朋友见面，到了地方之后彼此没有看到，你的反应更接近：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 249200, "title": "先等等没事的", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116125417NdbqSzRIj2T5ABg9.png"}, {"id": 249201, "title": "发条微信或短信", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116125441vaETedOLkxP83sFj.png"}, {"id": 249219, "title": "消息不回再打电话", "score": 1.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116134714oP63iBjrep0wKScH.jpg"}, {"id": 249220, "title": "直接打电话", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116134735LsjASlPg3zp54WEm.jpg"}]}, {"id": 3305, "content": "对于比较重要的事情（表白、辞职、分手……）你更经常使用的表达方法是：", "image": "", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 249312, "title": "嗯，找当事人面谈", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116171405H0LlGEKxd5sv4fBz.jpg"}, {"id": 249313, "title": "电话说，更及时点", "score": 0.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116172432xOXaeNRT1KzWi9dE.jpg"}, {"id": 249314, "title": "还是微信打字说吧", "score": 2.0, "image": "img/option/option/20171116171913iROBKytCeFJNwDhc.jpg"}, {"id": 249315, "title": "发个邮件忐忑等待", "score": 3.0, "image": "img/option/option/201711161724187gKVwxhCtfMRjSue.jpg"}]}]}